      "id": "szMwgK6hEieB23AMF26VO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -12.668342093595356,
      "y": 7282.589762461236,
      "width": 826.1636962890625,
      "height": 630,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b27",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 568834792,
      "version": 364,
      "versionNonce": 1226669032,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775146629011,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ALGORITHM \n\n1) Check if the list is empty \n    if Yes:\n            retun \" List is EMPTY\"\n\n    Otherwise :\n            temp= prev = head \n            traverse to the last node of the list\n            prev = second last node\n            temp = last node\n    \n    prev-> next = NULL\n    delete the temp node.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ALGORITHM \n\n1) Check if the list is empty \n    if Yes:\n            retun \" List is EMPTY\"\n\n    Otherwise :\n            temp= prev = head \n            traverse to the last node of the list\n            prev = second last node\n            temp = last node\n    \n    prev-> next = NULL\n    delete the temp node.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "W97xoG3bgUrAO2l3cvM3-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -109.71622288278098,
      "y": 8123.960614209383,
      "width": 914.0396728515625,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b28",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1330717928,
      "version": 75,
      "versionNonce": 732455656,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775146687425,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3) Delete from Index/middle/ intermediate position ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3) Delete from Index/middle/ intermediate position ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "lYTt5S7kE62-nSIFhF-Fr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -59.94260701838493,
      "y": 8283.579451291753,
      "width": 642.6357421875,
      "height": 810,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b29",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 516987288,
      "version": 431,
      "versionNonce": 1015189400,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775146940570,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Algorithm:\n\nCheck if the list is EMPTY or not \n    if yes: \n    then retun \" List is EMPTY\"\n\n    otherwise :\n    if(pos> 1  and pos< nodeCounter)\n\n    temp =  prev = head \n\n   while (nodeCounter  < pos)\n            prev = temp ;\n            temp = temp-> next l\n            nodeCounter ++;\n\n   prev -> next = temp -> next \n    delete the temp node",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Algorithm:\n\nCheck if the list is EMPTY or not \n    if yes: \n    then retun \" List is EMPTY\"\n\n    otherwise :\n    if(pos> 1  and pos< nodeCounter)\n\n    temp =  prev = head \n\n   while (nodeCounter  < pos)\n            prev = temp ;\n            temp = temp-> next l\n            nodeCounter ++;\n\n   prev -> next = temp -> next \n    delete the temp node",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
