      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Search an Element in Linked List \n\n\nALgo:\n\n*temp =  *head\npos = 1 \n    \n    while( temp != Null){\n    -> check if  temp-> data = TARGET\n                 if Yes :\n                            return pos\n                if NO:\n                   temp = temp -> next \n                    pos ++ ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Search an Element in Linked List \n\n\nALgo:\n\n*temp =  *head\npos = 1 \n    \n    while( temp != Null){\n    -> check if  temp-> data = TARGET\n                 if Yes :\n                            return pos\n                if NO:\n                   temp = temp -> next \n                    pos ++ ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
